PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784909938
OL,3,CSouthport killer transferred to
OL,4,Cpsychiatric hospital
OL,6,FSouthport killer Axel Rudakubana has
OL,7,Fbeen transferred from prison to
OL,8,FBroadmoor psychiatric hospital, the
OL,9,FMinistry of Justice has confirmed.
OL,11,FOfficials approved the transfer on
OL,12,Fbehalf of ministers, but a
OL,13,Fspokesperson for the department
OL,14,Fstressed it does not alter his 52-year
OL,15,Fsentence.
OL,17,FNext Wednesday marks two years since
OL,18,Fhe carried out an attack at a Taylor
OL,19,FSwift-themed dance class on July 29
OL,20,F2024, killing three girls and injuring
OL,21,Fmany others.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
