OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784909938
OL,3,CSouthport killer transferred to
OL,4,Cpsychiatric hospital
OL,6,FRudakubana, now 19, was given a life
OL,7,Fsentence for the murders of Alice da
OL,8,FSilva Aguiar, nine; Bebe King, six;
OL,9,Fand Elsie Dot Stancombe, seven, and
OL,10,Fthe attempted murder of eight other
OL,11,Fchildren and two adults.
OL,13,FHe's been moved to Broadmoor high
OL,14,Fsecurity hospital from the category A
OL,15,Fprison Belmarsh.
OL,17,FOffenders who present an increased
OL,18,Frisk, and cannot be managed safely in
OL,19,Fa prison environment because of mental
OL,20,Fdisorders, can be moved to secure
OL,21,Fpsychiatric units.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784909938
OL,3,CSouthport killer transferred to
OL,4,Cpsychiatric hospital
OL,6,FPeople in these units are treated as
OL,7,Fpatients rather than prisoners.
OL,9,FPatients in secure hospital units are
OL,10,Freported to cost more than #300,000
OL,11,Feach a year, compared to around
OL,12,F#60,000 for other prisoners.
OL,14,FThe MOJ spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,Ffamilies of those murdered and injured
OL,16,Fin Southport will be in this country's
OL,17,Fheart forever and our thoughts remain
OL,18,Fwith them.
OL,26,@vD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
