OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784909938
OL,3,CSouthport killer transferred to
OL,4,Cpsychiatric hospital
OL,6,F"Any decision to transfer an offender
OL,7,Fis made following an independent,
OL,8,Fclinical assessment, under the Mental
OL,9,FHealth Act. Following rigorous
OL,10,Fsecurity checks, the offender has been
OL,11,Ftransferred to a high-security
OL,12,Fpsychiatric unit, where he will remain
OL,13,Funtil assessed fit to return to prison.
OL,15,F"Officials have approved this
OL,16,Ftransfer, on behalf of Ministers. This
OL,17,Ftransfer does not change his sentence
OL,18,F` which remains at 52 years ` and of
OL,19,Fwhich he will serve every single day."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784909938
OL,3,CSouthport killer transferred to
OL,4,Cpsychiatric hospital
OL,6,FIn May last year, while at HMP
OL,7,FBelmarsh, Rudakubana allegedly
OL,8,Fattacked a prison officer with boiling
OL,9,Fwater using a kettle in his cell.
OL,11,FIn the years before the attack on the
OL,12,FSouthport dance class, three separate
OL,13,Freferrals were made to the
OL,14,FGovernment's anti-terror programme,
OL,15,FPrevent, about Rudakubana's behaviour,
OL,16,Fas well as six separate calls to
OL,17,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784909938
OL,3,CSouthport killer transferred to
OL,4,Cpsychiatric hospital
OL,6,FRudakubana attacked a pupil with a
OL,7,Fhockey stick, used school computers to
OL,8,Flook up the London Bridge terror
OL,9,Foutrage and carried a knife on a bus.
OL,11,FKnives, archery arrows and ricin, a
OL,12,Fbiological toxin 6,000 times more
OL,13,Fpoisonous than cyanide, were found
OL,14,Fwhen police raided Rudakubana's home
OL,15,Fafter the attack, with evidence
OL,16,Fsuggesting the equipment needed for
OL,17,Fthe substance was bought in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784909938
OL,3,CSouthport killer transferred to
OL,4,Cpsychiatric hospital
OL,6,FAlder Hey children's NHS foundation in
OL,7,FLiverpool previously confirmed he
OL,8,Freceived NHS mental health care
OL,9,Fbetween 2019 and 2023, when he
OL,10,F"stopped engaging".
OL,12,FBroadmoor, in Berkshire, is the oldest
OL,13,Fof the UK's three high-security
OL,14,Fhospitals and has held some of the
OL,15,FUK's most high-profile criminals,
OL,16,Fincluding Ronnie Kray and serial
OL,17,Fkiller Peter Sutcliffe, also known as
OL,18,Fthe Yorkshire Ripper.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
