OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784909938
OL,3,CSouthport killer transferred to
OL,4,Cpsychiatric hospital
OL,6,FUnder the Mental Health Act, officials
OL,7,Facting for the Justice Secretary have
OL,8,Fno choice but to accept the advice of
OL,9,Fclinical professionals to transfer
OL,10,Fprisoners to a secure facility.
OL,12,FAn offender in a secure hospital will
OL,13,Fbe compelled to engage with treatment
OL,14,Fand to undertake therapies before any
OL,15,Freturn to prison or release into the
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,18,FWhere offenders no longer require
OL,19,Ftreatment in hospital, the Act allows
OL,20,Fa swift return to prison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
